summary: Relating to certain structures, debris, machinery, and an automobile body on property in Blocks 34, 44, 55, 56, 57, 58, 59 & 65, Replat of Oneida Gardens Addition to Seattle; declaring the same to be a public nuisance, authorizing the summary abatement thereof, and making an appropriation from th Housing and Abatement Revolving Fund for the cost thereof.
